              >m</tei:supplied>it<tei:supplied>t</tei:supplied>ee for German
          Refugees</tei:rs><tei:lb/>San Francisco, California<tei:note xml:id="r0001-fn01"
            type="editorial" place="foot">The document from which this edition was made is a
            photocopy; the whereabouts of the original is not known. The sheet is torn down the left
            side, making beginnings of lines difficult to decipher. A carbon copy of this letter,
            unsigned, exists as LC ASC 7/50, [5] with envelope LC ASC 7/50, [5a] (transcribed here),
